{"id":275527,"date":[{"year":1952,"month":10,"day":29}],"page":"7","source":"“苏南日报”","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文化广场","column":"","genre":"","count":"256","ytitle":"","mtitle":"学好文化把家当","ftitle":"","authors":["汪中元"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪中元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)雄鸡叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鸡叫，天刚亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张家大哥就起床，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端着一张红板凳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天井里头读报章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂问:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“为啥起劲学文化?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大哥说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“学好文化把家当。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)月亮亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮亮，照四方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翠红姑娘细思量:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"速成识字真正好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我开眼瞎子他见了光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单字识了二千个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会读、会写、又会讲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化翻身那里来?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全亏恩人共产党!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)天上星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上星，亮晶晶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李家哥哥勿开心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加了速成识字班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥拼音拼勿准?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动脑筋，找竅门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来拼音有要领:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前音轻短后音重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两音相碰一齐冲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“勹——丫八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勹——ㄣ奔”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拼对字音才开心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(原载“苏南日报”)"}]}